sdelta requires the mhash library for generating sha1sum message digest.
mhash is available from
http://mhash.sourceforge.net
sdelta has been tested with mhash version 0.9.1
although newer or older versions may work fine.

export to the environment desired CFLAGS and LDFLAGS.

export   CFLAGS="-Os"

Will suffice on most platforms.

For Linux and Solaris: $ make
For FreeBSD:           $ make bsd
For All:               $ make install
